## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023, and some sources may have more recent updates that are not included. Additionally, the complexity of climate change impacts means that not all potential health effects are covered comprehensively. Further research is needed to explore regional variations and long-term health outcomes related to global warming.

